- What's up?
- I just wanted to get a little tipsy.

16
00:02:02,105 --> 00:02:03,709
Exactly...

17
00:02:03,709 --> 00:02:06,892
Why did you go to the get-together when you have panic disorder?

18
00:02:07,500 --> 00:02:09,567
I'm in trouble.

19
00:02:09,567 --> 00:02:10,776
What do you mean?

20
00:02:10,776 --> 00:02:14,334
I downed two bottles of soju...

21
00:02:15,670 --> 00:02:18,375
and I don't remember anything after that...

22
00:02:18,375 --> 00:02:22,510
You... came back at around 2 a.m.

23
00:02:22,510 --> 00:02:24,367
Around 2 a.m.?

24
00:02:27,025 --> 00:02:29,342
[Park Jong Hyeok: Bye, guys. (22:55)]
[Lee Min Gyeong: I had so much fun today!! (22:57)]

25
00:02:29,342 --> 00:02:32,218
[Team Leader Lee Hyo Rim: Get home safe, Guys! Please take care of Seung Jun! (22:58)]

26
00:02:35,167 --> 00:02:38,309
But based on the group chat, it ended at 11 p.m.

27
00:02:38,309 --> 00:02:40,225
Are you sure?

28
00:02:40,225 --> 00:02:41,859
Yes.

29
00:02:41,859 --> 00:02:47,800
