30
00:02:51,834 --> 00:02:55,034
[Song Jae Hyeon: Are you feeling a little better? (09:00)]

31
00:02:57,330 --> 00:02:59,000
What's wrong?

32
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:04,217
- Song Jae Hyeon?
- Song Jae Hyeon?

33
00:03:04,870 --> 00:03:06,934
What's going on?

34
00:03:18,660 --> 00:03:20,576
What do I do?

35
00:03:23,040 --> 00:03:25,096
Is it really all right for us to go?

36
00:03:25,096 --> 00:03:28,209
Of course. It's getting late. You guys should really be heading home.

37
00:03:28,209 --> 00:03:30,125
Okay, then we'll leave him to you.

38
00:03:30,125 --> 00:03:31,517
Bye!

39
00:03:31,517 --> 00:03:33,209
Don't worry. Have a good night.

40
00:03:33,209 --> 00:03:35,392
- See you.
- Yes.

41
00:03:36,459 --> 00:03:38,159
Ugh...

42
00:03:40,830 --> 00:03:42,850
I...

43
00:03:44,183 --> 00:03:47,500
I'm not usually like this.

44
00:03:49,580 --> 00:03:51,800
It's all because of...

45
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:54,840
that asshole.

46
00:03:55,459 --> 00:03:57,651
Asshole!

47
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:13,383
More...

48
00:04:13,383 --> 00:04:16,109
- What?
- I want more, please.

49
00:04:59,890 --> 00:05:02,134
Just a second.

50
00:05:05,530 --> 00:05:07,559
Put your shoe on.

51
00:05:15,148 --> 00:05:17,290
Which direction do we go from here?

52
00:05:18,250 --> 00:05:20,401
We're here.

53
00:05:28,887 --> 00:05:31,892
Thank you, Mr. Driver.

54
00:05:31,892 --> 00:05:34,726
Leave a message at that number,

55
00:05:34,726 --> 00:05:36,909
and I'll transfer the payment to you.

56
00:05:36,909 --> 00:05:39,517
I'm... not going anywhere!

57
00:05:39,517 --> 00:05:44,059
I live there. It's the house with the black door.

58
00:05:45,250 --> 00:05:46,613
[Vocal Trainer | Lee Seung Jun]

59
00:05:46,613 --> 00:05:50,118
I see you also give vocal lessons.
[Vocal Trainer | Lee Seung Jun]

60
00:05:50,118 --> 00:05:53,036
Then instead of the taxi fare, can I get lessons from you?

61
00:05:53,036 --> 00:05:55,070
Sure! I'd love to!

62
00:05:55,070 --> 00:05:57,486
I will... I will...

63
00:05:57,486 --> 00:05:59,653
I swear I'll give you vocal lessons! I will!

64
00:05:59,653 --> 00:06:01,362
Promise!

65
00:06:04,403 --> 00:06:07,578
Promise! Promise...

66
00:06:10,730 --> 00:06:13,186
Good night.

67
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:17,945
Here you go.

68
00:06:23,210 --> 00:06:26,854
Never mind... I'll just take you home.

69
00:06:27,830 --> 00:06:30,178
Be careful! Watch where you're going! Watch it.

70
00:06:30,178 --> 00:06:32,790
[Café Simsejeong]

71
00:06:42,570 --> 00:06:44,945
Your Einspänner is ready.
(T/N: Viennese black coffee with whipped cream)

72
00:06:45,710 --> 00:06:48,495
Can I get some napkins?

73
00:06:49,190 --> 00:06:51,703
I want more, please

74
00:06:59,780 --> 00:07:01,547
More?

75
00:07:01,547 --> 00:07:03,897
Yes, much more.

76
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:07,912
Enjoy your drink.

77
00:07:17,730 --> 00:07:19,870
You're seeing someone, aren't you?

78
00:07:20,790 --> 00:07:22,611
What are you talking about?

79
00:07:22,611 --> 00:07:24,378
I'm not seeing anyone!

80
00:07:24,378 --> 00:07:26,887
You've been smiling since this morning.

81
00:07:26,887 --> 00:07:29,319
Right! We have eyes, you know.

82
00:07:29,319 --> 00:07:30,862
I have not.

83
00:07:30,862 --> 00:07:33,295
I wonder how long it will last this time.

84
00:07:33,295 --> 00:07:36,070
Did you guys finish the things I told you to do or not?

85
00:07:36,070 --> 00:07:37,862
- Of course we did!
- We did!

86
00:07:37,862 --> 00:07:39,885
Then what's the mess here?

87
00:07:39,885 --> 00:07:43,580
Those just came in, so we were just about to start!

88
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:48,520
[Rhythm J]

89
00:07:48,520 --> 00:07:50,450
♫ I'm going crazy ♫

90
00:07:50,450 --> 00:07:54,900
♫ Even when you're not doing anything ♫

91
00:07:54,900 --> 00:07:59,160
♫ You have that power ♫

92
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:03,910
♫ From head to toe, whenever I see you ♫

93
00:08:03,910 --> 00:08:08,330
♫ I think I'll go crazy ♫

94
00:08:08,330 --> 00:08:11,780
♫ Come on! We won't give up this time ♫

95
00:08:13,330 --> 00:08:15,910
♫ Wow ♫

96
00:08:17,260 --> 00:08:19,910
♫ Come on! We won't give up this time ♫

97
00:08:44,640 --> 00:08:46,230
What are you watching so seriously?

98
00:08:46,230 --> 00:08:48,172
Teacher!

99
00:08:48,172 --> 00:08:49,686
Don't you know Kim Chan Wu?

100
00:08:49,686 --> 00:08:52,419
He's all over the Internet and the news.

101
00:08:52,419 --> 00:08:54,836
Take a look, he's the talk of the town.

102
00:08:54,836 --> 00:08:57,612
Later. Let's start class.

103
00:08:57,612 --> 00:08:59,503
Did you do your warm-ups?

104
00:08:59,503 --> 00:09:02,661
No, not at all.

105
00:09:03,660 --> 00:09:07,964
Teacher, is it true that they'll be attending our academy?

106
00:09:07,964 --> 00:09:09,878
I don't know.

107
00:09:09,878 --> 00:09:12,145
What? I got my hopes up for nothing.

108
00:09:12,145 --> 00:09:16,678
Why doesn't our academy have any idol stars or trainees? So many other academies do.

109
00:09:16,678 --> 00:09:18,661
Scales first.

110
00:09:18,661 --> 00:09:20,395
Okay.

111
00:09:25,145 --> 00:09:27,595
[Song Jae Hyeon: Seung Jun, are you busy?]

112
00:09:32,036 --> 00:09:35,554
[Song Jae Hyeon: Are you feeling a little better? Seung Jun, are you busy?]

113
00:09:40,220 --> 00:09:41,590
[Vocal Trainer | Lee Seung Jun]

114
00:09:43,536 --> 00:09:46,478
Hyeon Ji, I'll head home first. Can you close up for me?

115
00:09:46,478 --> 00:09:47,728
What? Already?

116
00:09:47,728 --> 00:09:50,196
I'll open tomorrow. See you.

117
00:09:50,196 --> 00:09:53,629
Umm... Okay, see you tomorrow!

118
00:09:55,062 --> 00:09:57,511
Is he going on a date?

119
00:09:58,365 --> 00:10:00,857
It seems a bit different this time...

120
00:10:00,857 --> 00:10:02,770
I'm betting it'll only last for a month.

121
00:10:02,770 --> 00:10:05,462
Two weeks for me.

122
00:10:16,978 --> 00:10:22,153
[Song Jae Hyeon: Seung Jun, you haven't replied to my texts, and I'm getting worried. Is everything all right?]

123
00:10:24,153 --> 00:10:27,745
No, I'm just...

124
00:10:30,187 --> 00:10:31,903
No.

125
00:10:32,450 --> 00:10:35,461
Taking the meds...

126
00:10:35,461 --> 00:10:37,820
It's a bit much, isn't it?

127
00:10:54,245 --> 00:10:56,078
Seung Jun!

128
00:10:59,070 --> 00:11:01,495
Why are you here...

129
00:11:01,495 --> 00:11:04,045
You're on your way home, right?

130
00:11:04,828 --> 00:11:07,319
I'm just on time.

131
00:11:07,319 --> 00:11:10,693
I noticed that your academy was quite close to the café.

132
00:11:12,105 --> 00:11:16,000
I was worried because you didn't reply.

133
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:18,661
I wanted to apologize properly.

134
00:11:18,661 --> 00:11:21,162
I'm sorry for asking rude questions yesterday.

135
00:11:21,162 --> 00:11:24,678
It's fine. I'm the one who made a mistake.

136
00:11:24,678 --> 00:11:27,637
I was just trying to get more friendly with you.

137
00:11:27,637 --> 00:11:30,911
I hope there weren't any misunderstandings.

138
00:11:30,911 --> 00:11:32,555
Of course.

139
00:11:34,803 --> 00:11:36,378
Wait...

140
00:11:45,703 --> 00:11:47,053
Hyeong!

141
00:11:47,053 --> 00:11:49,719
Why are you so surprised?

142
00:11:49,719 --> 00:11:51,603
You finished late today.

143
00:11:51,603 --> 00:11:53,270
Did you wait for me?

144
00:11:53,270 --> 00:11:54,580
Yes.

145
00:11:54,580 --> 00:11:57,136
Have you eaten? Let's go get something tasty.

146
00:11:57,136 --> 00:12:01,162
Ah... I'd love to, but I have to go practice.

147
00:12:01,162 --> 00:12:04,344
- I told your manager that you'll be a little late.
- Pardon?

148
00:12:04,344 --> 00:12:07,828
I said that you had an important meeting to attend, so don't worry.

149
00:12:07,828 --> 00:12:09,746
What are we having?

150
00:12:09,746 --> 00:12:11,487
Come on.

151
00:12:21,909 --> 00:12:25,634
Do you want to have dinner together?

152
00:12:27,806 --> 00:12:29,655
I'm sorry.

153
00:12:39,817 --> 00:12:43,279
The guy who made me such a mess...

154
00:12:43,279 --> 00:12:49,411
I became defensive in both social and romantic relationships after I met him.

155
00:12:49,411 --> 00:12:54,519
He left a stain, and the more I tried to rub it away, the more it spread.

156
00:13:11,178 --> 00:13:14,762
I'll drive you home, let's go.

157
00:14:17,149 --> 00:14:19,734
There's probably something similar about him.

158
00:14:19,734 --> 00:14:21,757
Why did I make such a stupid mistake?

159
00:14:21,757 --> 00:14:22,803
That's it.

160
00:14:22,803 --> 00:14:24,432
And you just came home?

161
00:14:24,432 --> 00:14:26,865
Relinquish your feelings for him for now.

162
00:14:26,865 --> 00:14:28,240
You should have just said it.

163
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:31,240
Right... Oh... Wait, was I that obvious?

164
00:14:31,240 --> 00:14:33,115
Why would you ask m─

165
00:14:33,115 --> 00:14:36,457
Does that actually work even when they're not interested?

166
00:14:36,457 --> 00:14:39,449
Tell me... Have we met before?

167
00:14:39,449 --> 00:14:41,549
Right?

168
00:14:41,549 --> 00:14:43,590
Seung Jun!
